:vsplit -- split vertically
C-(g,h,j,k) -- navigate to different tab
u -- undo
p -- paste
i -- insert
dnd -- delete n rows below
dd -- delete line
yy -- yank /copy line
e -- move forword to the end of line
w -- move forward to the start of line
A -- insert at the end of the line
TEXT -------------
a] arround [...]
i] inner [...]

ya] --- yank around[...] 
o	Begin a new line below the cursor
O	Begin a new line above the cursor
r{text}	Replace the character under the cursor with {text}
R	Replace characters instead of inserting them

ysiw) = add surrounging inner word () // surroung word with ()
